{%- comment -%}
  Shelzy's Designs - Care Instructions Page Section
  Comprehensive guide to caring for sublimation water bottles
{%- endcomment -%}

<section class="sz-care-section">
  <div class="sz-care-container">

    {%- comment -%} Header {%- endcomment -%}
    <header class="sz-care-header">
      <h1 class="sz-care-title">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h1>
      <p class="sz-care-subtitle">{{ section.settings.subheading }}</p>
    </header>

    {%- comment -%} Key Points Banner {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="sz-care-banner">
      <div class="sz-care-banner-item">
        <span class="sz-care-icon">&#10003;</span>
        <span>Dishwasher Safe</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sz-care-banner-item">
        <span class="sz-care-icon">&#10003;</span>
        <span>No Peeling Ever</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sz-care-banner-item">
        <span class="sz-care-icon">&#10003;</span>
        <span>Permanent Print</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%} Care Content {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="sz-care-content">

      <div class="sz-care-card">
        <h2 class="sz-care-card-title">Why Sublimation is Different</h2>
        <p>Unlike vinyl or stickers that sit on top of the surface, our sublimation printing infuses the ink directly into the coating of the bottle. This means:</p>
        <ul class="sz-care-list">
          <li><strong>No peeling</strong> &mdash; the design is part of the bottle</li>
          <li><strong>No fading</strong> &mdash; colors stay vibrant wash after wash</li>
          <li><strong>No cracking</strong> &mdash; flexes with the material</li>
          <li><strong>Dishwasher safe</strong> &mdash; top rack recommended</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sz-care-card">
        <h2 class="sz-care-card-title">Daily Care</h2>
        <ul class="sz-care-list">
          <li>Hand wash or place on the <strong>top rack of your dishwasher</strong></li>
          <li>Use mild soap &mdash; avoid abrasive scrubbers</li>
          <li>Rinse thoroughly after each use</li>
          <li>Allow to air dry completely before storing</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sz-care-card">
        <h2 class="sz-care-card-title">What to Avoid</h2>
        <ul class="sz-care-list">
          <li><strong>Microwaving</strong> &mdash; stainless steel is not microwave safe</li>
          <li><strong>Freezing with liquid inside</strong> &mdash; expansion may damage the bottle</li>
          <li><strong>Bleach or harsh chemicals</strong> &mdash; may affect the coating over time</li>
          <li><strong>Steel wool or abrasive pads</strong> &mdash; may scratch the surface</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sz-care-card">
        <h2 class="sz-care-card-title">Temperature Tips</h2>
        <p>Our double-wall vacuum insulated bottles are designed to:</p>
        <ul class="sz-care-list">
          <li>Keep drinks <strong>cold for 24 hours</strong></li>
          <li>Keep drinks <strong>hot for 12 hours</strong></li>
          <li>Work best when pre-chilled or pre-warmed with water first</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="sz-care-note">Pro tip: Add ice before your drink for maximum cold retention!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="sz-care-card">
        <h2 class="sz-care-card-title">Deep Cleaning</h2>
        <p>For occasional deep cleaning or odor removal:</p>
        <ol class="sz-care-list sz-care-numbered">
          <li>Fill bottle with warm water and 1 tablespoon of baking soda</li>
          <li>Let sit for 15&ndash;30 minutes</li>
          <li>Scrub gently with a bottle brush</li>
          <li>Rinse thoroughly and air dry</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="sz-care-note">For stubborn odors, add a splash of white vinegar to the baking soda mixture.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="sz-care-card sz-care-card-highlight">
        <h2 class="sz-care-card-title">Our Quality Promise</h2>
        <p>Every Shelzy's Designs bottle is handcrafted with care using premium sublimation printing. We stand behind our products &mdash; if you ever have an issue with your design, please <a href="/pages/contact">contact us</a> and we'll make it right.</p>
        <div class="sz-care-cta">
          <a href="/collections/best-sellers" class="sz-btn-primary">Shop Best Sellers</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

{% style %}
  .sz-care-section {
    padding: 60px 24px 80px;
    background: var(--sz-white, #FFFFFF);
  }

  .sz-care-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .sz-care-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .sz-care-title {
    font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }

  .sz-care-subtitle {
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #666;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Key Points Banner */
  .sz-care-banner {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 32px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding: 24px;
    background: #F5F7F4;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .sz-care-banner-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .sz-care-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    background: #fb5887;
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  /* Content Cards */
  .sz-care-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .sz-care-card {
    padding: 32px;
    background: #fefefe;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .sz-care-card-highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fb5887 0%, #fb5887 100%);
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .sz-care-card-highlight .sz-care-card-title {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .sz-care-card-highlight a {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .sz-care-card-title {
    font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .sz-care-card p {
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #555;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .sz-care-card-highlight p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  .sz-care-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0 0 0 20px;
  }

  .sz-care-list li {
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .sz-care-numbered {
    list-style-type: decimal;
  }

  .sz-care-note {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #fb5887;
    margin-top: 16px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    background: rgba(139, 170, 136, 0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .sz-care-cta {
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .sz-btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    background: #FFFFFF;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .sz-btn-primary:hover {
    background: #F5F5F5;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .sz-care-section {
      padding: 40px 16px 60px;
    }

    .sz-care-banner {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .sz-care-card {
      padding: 24px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Care Instructions",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "sz-care-page-section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "Care Instructions"
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "subheading",
      "label": "Subheading",
      "default": "Everything you need to know about caring for your personalized sublimation water bottle."
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Care Instructions"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
